One important goal for any business is to break even, which means generating enough revenue

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,160
to cover your expenses.

3
00:00:07,160 --> 00:00:13,120
To achieve this, you may need to shell out some funds up front to invest in key resources

4
00:00:13,120 --> 00:00:14,640
and bring in customers.

5
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:20,280
However, it's important to balance these expenses with your overall financial health

6
00:00:20,280 --> 00:00:22,880
to ensure you don't go under.

7
00:00:22,880 --> 00:00:28,920
By setting realistic goals, investing wisely and staying focused on your objectives, you

8
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:33,720
can work towards building a successful and sustainable business.

